'''''Arende''''', ni Sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo 1994 iyobowe na Dirk de Villiers <ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Arende</ref>.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Ian Roberts na Gavin van den Berg mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Diane Wilson, Keith Grenville na Percy Sieff mu nshingano zabo<ref>https://mubi.com/films/arende</ref>.<ref>https://www.moviefone.com/movie/arende/ypipj0znWvCNzx8bOigwk6/main/</ref> 

Iyi filime ivuga ibyerekeranye n’Intambara ya Anglo Boer nubuzima bwumuhinzi wigometse Boer Sloet Steenkamp na Kapiteni wingabo [[Ubwongereza|zUbwongereza]] James Kerwin.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://mubi.com/films/arende</ref><ref>https://filmoria.co.uk/movie-list/arende-mv0176169</ref> 

